Products.Name: Robt Roberts Rooibos Tea 40'S 100G
Products.Description:
Uniquely aromatic and naturally caffeine free 'Red Bush' tea from the Western Cape Province in South Africa.

Rooibos, meaning 'Red Bush' in Afrikaans, originates from the Cederberg area of the Western Cape Province in South Africa. The needle like leaves of the 'Aspalathus Linearis' plant are chopped, bruised and left out in the South African sun to dry, a process which gives Rooibos its distinctive reddish-brown colour and warm aromatic flavour.
